    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This isn't just a car; it\u2019s a time machine carved from chrome and dreams. Imagine yourself behind the wheel, the scent of hand-stitched leather and nostalgia swirling in the air as you chase the golden hour. Every curve of its mirror-finish body catches the light like a rare jewel, a testament to an era when craftsmanship was a sacred art. Preserved like a masterpiece in a private gallery, this vehicle whispers stories of sun-drenched coastal drives and moonlit escapes. It is a rare opportunity to own a piece of automotive poetry that feels as vibrant and pristine today as the moment it first graced the asphalt.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
